WEBVTT
X-TIMESTAMP-MAP=MPEGTS:181083,LOCAL:00:00:00.000

00:22:59.626 --> 00:23:02.246 A:middle
Let's book this travel.

00:23:02.326 --> 00:23:02.586 A:middle
Great.

00:23:03.296 --> 00:23:07.466 A:middle
Now, let me summarize what we

00:23:07.466 --> 00:23:07.916 A:middle
talked about.

00:23:13.386 --> 00:23:15.036 A:middle
So, to make our app layout great

00:23:15.036 --> 00:23:16.826 A:middle
for our global audience, there

00:23:16.826 --> 00:23:18.366 A:middle
are a few simple steps.

00:23:18.996 --> 00:23:20.246 A:middle
First, is to use high level

00:23:20.246 --> 00:23:21.496 A:middle
containers like StackView

00:23:21.496 --> 00:23:23.066 A:middle
whenever possible, as they

00:23:23.066 --> 00:23:24.396 A:middle
provide a lot of heavy lifting

00:23:24.396 --> 00:23:24.866 A:middle
for you.

00:23:25.526 --> 00:23:26.706 A:middle
And believe me, they are just

00:23:26.706 --> 00:23:27.506 A:middle
simpler to use.

00:23:28.506 --> 00:23:30.146 A:middle
For finer control, remember to

00:23:30.146 --> 00:23:31.936 A:middle
use Auto Layout and make sure to

00:23:31.936 --> 00:23:33.186 A:middle
use leading and trailing

00:23:33.186 --> 00:23:34.976 A:middle
constraint so that you can adapt

00:23:34.976 --> 00:23:36.016 A:middle
for right to left languages.

00:23:37.016 --> 00:23:38.546 A:middle
For early testing without even

00:23:38.546 --> 00:23:40.396 A:middle
localizing your app, you can use

00:23:40.396 --> 00:23:42.136 A:middle
the pseudolanguages in Xcode

00:23:42.136 --> 00:23:42.786 A:middle
Scheme Editor.

00:23:43.556 --> 00:23:44.886 A:middle
And please, don't ignore the

00:23:44.886 --> 00:23:45.996 A:middle
Auto Layout warnings in the

00:23:45.996 --> 00:23:46.796 A:middle
Interface Builder.

00:23:47.246 --> 00:23:48.456 A:middle
They are very useful for

00:23:48.456 --> 00:23:50.486 A:middle
avoiding clipping, truncation,

00:23:50.486 --> 00:23:51.606 A:middle
and overlapping issues.

00:23:52.516 --> 00:23:54.286 A:middle
Now, over to Karan to talk about

00:23:54.566 --> 00:23:54.876 A:middle
text.

00:23:55.016 --> 00:23:57.000 A:middle
[ Applause ]

00:23:57.276 --> 00:23:58.006 A:middle
&gt;&gt; Thank you, Dongyuan.

00:23:58.946 --> 00:24:00.306 A:middle
Good morning, everyone.

